# Cursor Rule: No root docs/

- Root `docs/` directory is forbidden in this repository.
- Global documentation lives in `docs_project/`
- Module documentation lives in `Modules/<Module>/docs/`
- All filenames in any docs/ folder must be lowercase (except README.md)

## Validation
- Run `bashscripts/docs/validate-no-root-docs.sh` locally and in CI.
- If it fails, migrate content to `docs_project/_legacy_root_docs/` and remove the root `docs/` directory.
